text: "Overjoyed" is a 1985 song by Stevie Wonder. It was taken from his 20th studio album In Square Circle. It went to number 10 in Ireland, number 17 in the United Kingdom, number 24 in the United States, number 33 in Belgium and number 55 in Canada.
